sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant BBR as BBR ext-proc Service<br/>9004/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant MPR as model-provider-resolver<br/>Plugin
    participant AT as api-translation<br/>Plugin
    participant AKI as apikey-injection<br/>Plugin
    participant NRQ as nemo-request-guard<br/>Plugin
    participant NRS as nemo-response-guard<br/>Plugin
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NeMo as NeMo Guardrails<br/>HTTP
    participant Provider as External LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 1: Inference Request Processing

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{ns}/{model}/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Gateway-level auth
    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc request<br/>gRPC/9004, plaintext (mesh-internal)

    BBR->>MPR: Process request body
    MPR->>K8s: Watch ExternalModel CRs<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>MPR: ExternalModel spec (provider, model, format)
    MPR-->>BBR: CycleState: provider info set

    BBR->>AT: Translate request
    Note over AT: In-process translation<br/>OpenAI→Anthropic/Azure/Bedrock/Vertex
    AT-->>BBR: CycleState: translated body

    BBR->>AKI: Inject API key
    AKI->>K8s: Watch labeled Secrets<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>AKI: Secret data (api-key)
    AKI-->>BBR: Auth header injected

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 2: NeMo Content Moderation (optional)

    BBR->>NRQ: Check request content
    NRQ->>NeMo: POST /v1/rails/check<br/>HTTP, configurable port
    NeMo-->>NRQ: Allow / Block
    alt Blocked
        NRQ-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
        Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 1 continued: Forward to provider

    Gateway->>Provider: POST inference request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+ (Istio SIMPLE origination)<br/>Provider API key header
    Provider-->>Gateway: Inference response

    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc response
    BBR->>NRS: Check response content
    NRS->>NeMo: POST /v1/rails/check<br/>HTTP, configurable port
    NeMo-->>NRS: Allow / Block
    BBR->>AT: Translate response
    Note over AT: Reverse translation<br/>Anthropic/Azure/Bedrock/Vertex→OpenAI
    AT-->>BBR: Translated response body
    BBR-->>Gateway: Processed response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 3: ExternalProvider Reconciliation

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over K8s: Controller watches ExternalProvider CRDs
        K8s->>K8s: ExternalProvider CR created/updated
        K8s-->>BBR: Watch event
        BBR->>K8s: GET Secret (credentials)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
        K8s-->>BBR: Secret data
        BBR->>K8s: Create/Update Service (ExternalName)<br/>HTTPS/443
        BBR->>K8s: Create/Update Istio ServiceEntry<br/>HTTPS/443
        BBR->>K8s: Create/Update Istio DestinationRule<br/>HTTPS/443
    end
